A customer satisfaction survey was conducted at a store, and the scores on customer service were recorded on a scale of 1-10 for each customer. Use cluster analysis with k-means to group the customers into two distinct clusters based on their satisfaction scores, where k=2.

The scores are as follows: {8, 7, 4, 6, 9, 5, 3, 2, 7, 8, 9, 10, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 6, 5, 4, 3, 6, 7, 5}

What are the two clusters and what are the mean scores of the two clusters?
